{"tid":1115122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講開Sammi喺90年代係咪最紅天后  王菲其實應該紅啲！","createTime":"2019-04-19T03:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T07:29:50.000Z","uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2fe3e799130689d9344a427a3f856178df65939","tid":1115122,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日00後應該覺得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">王菲</span></strong>只係謝霆鋒條年上女，係<strong>大陸阿嬋歌手</strong>，亦唔知邊個係王靖雯，更無興趣知竇靖童個老豆係邊個，覺得佢同香港無乜關係好離身。<br />\n<br />\n的確係嘅，自從佢搬返上老家北京後，又唔出廣東歌又唔會喺電視出現，玩微博唔玩public ig，對支那嘢無興趣自然對佢無興趣。但查實回帶返30年前，其實佢當時係喺香港出道，唱地道廣東歌，個藝名叫王靖雯(Shirley)好港式，一手帶佢入行嘅歌唱老師都非常港式，係80,90年代好多人想佢帶出道(因為好多都紅咗，又入到大公司)嘅戴斯聰(00後90後應唔知佢係乜水)。 <br />\n<br />\n87年來港，89年參加「亞太金箏流行曲創作大賽」，歌曲《仍是舊句子》獲得銅獎，佢負責唱，當時腔口仲係字正腔圓有啲娘，但把聲就真係好J到爆。無幾耐佢就出碟，有幾首幾HIT嘅歌，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《無奈那天》《EVERYTHING》《多得他》</span></strong>等，但始終係二線。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHjhnQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHjhnQo.jpg&h=fa6b622f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz41Pvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz41Pvp.jpg&h=347eae87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CN-t0A7G7Lo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCN-t0A7G7Lo&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=aa656326\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CN-t0A7G7Lo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7JzfptrpFFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7JzfptrpFFo&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=b03ec7f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7JzfptrpFFo</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">王菲 &amp; 林憶蓮經典version - 多得他</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一來當時好多前輩仲係衝緊，二來佢都未建立到個人特色，極其量係把聲幾正幾唱得咁。 無幾耐仲話去美國，原來當時佢嘅公司新藝寶改組，將佢嘅經理人約賣出，佢輾轉由陳小寶到羅大佑，最後自己找上新經理人陳家瑛。 <br />\n<br />\n其實當時佢係大陸出身，來港前做過啲濕九MODEL，扮吓鄧麗君出過下碟。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/7f2e5fec971c4bf482509f106487ace8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181112%2F7f2e5fec971c4bf482509f106487ace8.gif&h=6208773e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFP5wK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFP5wK2.jpg&h=5469976d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般都覺得佢有陣阿燦(死語)娘味，個個睇漏眼。到92年，佢以全身型像返港，出碟叫<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《Coming Home》</span></strong>，走R &amp; B路線，中文名仲係娘娘地叫靖雯，但英文名就由Shirley改做Faye，密密起革命。其實改得好啱，當時另一Shirley關淑怡紅過佢。 此碟開頭Plug《Miss You Night And Day》，開首長長嘅一段拉音技驚四座 ，不過令佢大紅嘅，係碟中另一首，改自中島美雪嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《容易受傷的女人》</span></strong>。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rOGbYAEOmxk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrOGbYAEOmxk&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=73fb0289\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rOGbYAEOmxk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16vc92H1EgA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D16vc92H1EgA&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=4955d7cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16vc92H1EgA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BMutSuCiIjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBMutSuCiIjM&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=bae9b9d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BMutSuCiIjM</a><br />\n<br />\n紅咗，上咗一線，佢終於可對自己嘅碟多啲意見，93年嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《執迷不悔》</span></strong>，首次負責封面概念，寫了她第一首國語歌《執迷不悔（國語版）》，開始唱佢最熟嘅母語歌，除咗專輯同名歌外，又紅咗首《季候風》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zP8qnnZMs8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzP8qnnZMs8Q&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=1047e7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zP8qnnZMs8Q</a><br />\n[url][<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3FlmCHYeINw[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3FlmCHYeINw%5B%2Furl%5D&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=4061eb7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3FlmCHYeINw[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n 直到同年第6張大碟<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《十萬個為什麼？》(</span></strong>紅咗《如風》《冷戰》《Summer Of Love》<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《流非飛》</span></strong>(菲菲不停問我，飛自由，完全飛自由)，好明顯佢好想用返真名 ，不過此碟仍係用王靖雯個名出），形象，歌路亦型咗。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmHSbJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmHSbJ5.jpg&h=72bec75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3K7oTLjtbaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3K7oTLjtbaU&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=0f2f5749\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3K7oTLjtbaU</a><br />\n<br />\n太長待續"},{"pid":"045ccfc8cb5151680c0a4bd5804474df05cc766a","tid":1115122,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"阿婆"},{"pid":"7ed144db4d1c79d808b054531e76a2a5f2a75733","tid":1115122,"uid":799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"王菲紅90年代頭，sammi紅90年代尾"},{"pid":"77037176cfb5de4ff537df0782c3f46a3a83e36e","tid":1115122,"uid":92377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"呢邊無人應"},{"pid":"9ba81dcab81efc5dacc6ae976095dd34af495331","tid":1115122,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"留名待睇<br />\n樓主紀錄好仔細"},{"pid":"795cbbf21463eb1026fdfbe2c2e769359a272c37","tid":1115122,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"係戴思聰，唔係戴斯聰"},{"pid":"ef8ac50ee0b2986abaa36f70ce1a7962c47183b5","tid":1115122,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795cbbf21463eb1026fdfbe2c2e769359a272c37","tid":1115122,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"係戴思聰，唔係戴斯聰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"你錯啦<br />\n佢自己話係斯㗎之前訪問<br />\n一直俾人誤寫"},{"pid":"7a4fafc76da04a555b91a49d7ffdec8552d74403","tid":1115122,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba81dcab81efc5dacc6ae976095dd34af495331","tid":1115122,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"留名待睇<br />\n樓主紀錄好仔細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"講開Sammi喺90年代係咪最紅天后 王菲其實應該紅啲！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hwppDsX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hwppDsX</a><br />\n去衣邊啦<br />\nkij<br />\n<br />\n我唔小心開咗2個之前<br />\n這邊多人好多 <br />\n仲有#184寫咗第二篇"}]}